have received, you have a money-back guarantee. These flexible contract terms, combined with excellent price transparency, help make Link Interactive one of the best values among home security systems.","Although <a href=\"/lifeshield-security-review\">LifeShield</a> and <a href=\"/simplisafe-review\">SimpliSafe</a> both offer more affordable monitoring and no-fee cancellation, we feel that Link Interactive&#39;s superior equipment selection and similar starting costs make it a better value."]},"id":"6d67554e-bb0a-47d4-b64f-51c28692a9ac","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/JUenspQem5g9KtucEoettL.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/68142-link-interactive6.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JUenspQem5g9KtucEoettL.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"JUenspQem5g9KtucEoettL","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JUenspQem5g9KtucEoettL.jpg","alt":""},"id":"da9a2e4e-bd3b-484c-b113-4819093b68a7","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The equipment comes pre-programmed and you must install it yourself. You can build your own custom system if you want, choosing equipment from Link Interactive&#39;s plentiful supply. Among other things, you can choose from several types of security cameras, a touchscreen deadbolt, recessed door and window sensors, a remote panic button and more. A three-year warranty complements the contract length and is average for a home security system.","For customer service, Link Interactive provides installation video tutorials along with customer support through email, phone and live chat. The company also responds to public and private messages on social media. Our experiences with Link Interactive were pleasant and worthwhile. We did not get a hard sell, although one representative did refer repeatedly to a promotion the company was offering at the time."]},"id":"c9b601f0-abbd-41ec-be47-9bc9b80ad780","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"